sentences: Julia Mikhaylovna Lezhneva (Russian: Юлия Михайловна Лежнева; born 5 December 1989) is a Russian soprano opera singer and recitalist, specialising in soprano and coloratura mezzo-soprano material of the 18th and early 19th century.
In 2004, Lezhneva graduated with distinction from the Gretchaninov Music School in Moscow.
